  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a small pan over medium heat.",
    "Add smoked paprika and stir for 30 seconds to release aroma.",
    "Add tamarind paste and cook for 1 minute until thickened.",
    "Add sliced sweet red peppers and cook for 5 minutes until tender.",
    "Stir in coconut milk and cook for 2 minutes until silky.",
    "Add chopped cilantro and mix gently.",
    "Serve immediately with a sprinkle of extra smoked paprika."
